Package: cartogram.advisor
Title: Warn Against Inappropriate Use of Cartograms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Detects non-extensive spatial variables that are inappropriate
    for area cartograms by fitting a generalised additive model and testing
    whether the area-scaling exponent is significantly below one.  Intended
    as the statistical back-end for a cartogram warning feature in
    go-cart.io.
